<p>An element, much like a <span class="script">template.XULElem("button")</span>, that is placed on a <span class="script">template.XULElem("menubar")</span>. When the user clicks the <code>menu</code> element, the child <span class="script">template.XULElem("menupopup")</span> of the menu will be displayed. This element is also used to create submenus.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Simple_Menu_Bars" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Simple_Menu_Bars">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
